wordpressPost.excerpt: All other kinds of tickets are now sold out

Week passes and day passes for Wednesday, Friday and Saturday are now sold out.

Thursday 8th of August– Tame Impala / Sigrid / Earl Sweatshirt / Erykah Badu / Ricochets / Hot Snakes / Mitski / Pond / Kommode / Protoje & The Indiggnation / Sushi & Kobe / Koffee / Baba Stiltz / FONTAINES D.C. / Farao / Saoirse +++
